      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Yasha. ?] Then was born in the-- a daughter, Fiena, and we got three children.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
